    RabbitMQ -->|"sensor.updated events"| PythonAlert

    GoAlert -->|"GET /sensors/:id\n(circuit breaker)"| GoSvc
    PythonAlert -->|"GET /sensors/:id\n(retries + timeout)"| PythonSvc

